quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan mofte maa …óen: Allah wahayinii e am, wonnde dental jinna he…óitike lam Ba·π≠nu Nakhlah, mi…óo jannga Alqur'aanaa. Nde …ói ruttinoo ka jamaa majji, …ói wi'ani …óin : Menen men nani konngol hino janngee, haawniingol e …ìannginol e laa…ìugol mun."
  72,2,"Ngol konngol ngol men nani, hino fewnira e peewal ka fi…ìnde, e ka konngol e ka kuugal. Men gom…óinii nde. Men kafidataa e Joomi amen jippin…óo nde On, hay e gooto."
  72,3,"Men gom…óinirii Mo, tawde manngural Joomi amen ngal toowii, O siforaali jogitagol …ìeyngu, wanaa …ìi…ó…óo."
  72,4,"E wonnde Ibuliisa hino wowlaynoo peenale e hoore Allah, …ìe dammba genndo …ìi…ó…óo e Makko."
  72,5,"Menen men sikkuo wonnde sirkoo…ìe yim…ìe e jinna …ìen wonah fenaande wowlunoo, fewndo …ìe aa∆¥inoo wonnde Allah no jogitii genndo e …ìi…ó…óo. Men goongini …ìe men jokki …ìe."
  72,6,"Hari ado islaamu, wor…ìe yim…ìe goo hino mooloraynoo wor…ìe jinna goo, tuma kala …ìe hewti e nokku hul…ìinii…óo, nanaa hi…ìe wi'a: mi moolorii koohoojo ndee aynde, immorde e bone …óaytu…ìe yim…ìe mun …ìen. Wor…ìe yim…ìe …ìen …ìeydii hulugol …óe∆¥noo wor…ìe jinna …ìen."
  72,7,"Yim…ìe …ìen sikkir no sikkir…óon non onon jinnaaji …óin, wonnde Allah immintintaa hay gooto fii √±aaweede yo…ìitee, …ìaawo maayde mun."
  72,8,"Men tefuno fii kammu ngun, men tawi hingu hebbiniraa Malaa'ka aynoo…ìe tii…óu…ìe, ko ayna ko men he…óitotonoo kon. Ngu hebbiniraa kadi yiite ko fi…óiree kala …ìadii…óo ngu."
  72,9,"Hari me…óen joo…óotonoo ka kammu ton fii he…óagol ko Malaa'ika'en wowlata, men he…ìa ko men humpita nduree…ìe leydi ndin, kono …óum wayiima. Kala he…óitii…óo e amen jooni, o hawray e docotal yiite, no o …ìadori, ngal sunna mo."
  72,10,"E wonnde men anndaa sabu ngol aygnugol kammu ngun. Hara ko bone faandoraa yim…ìe leydi ndin? Kaa hara Allah faandani …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere. Kumpite kammu ngun majjitorike men."
  72,11,"E wonnde menen jinnaaji …óin, hino e amen gom…óu…ói …óiggu…ói, hino e amen kadi keeferi naafiqiiji. Hari ko men nooneeji seertu…ói."
  72,12,"E wonnde men yanano men laawotaako Allah senii…óo On, si O faandanike men huunde, ko non kadi men laawortaa Mo dogugol, tawde Himo hu…ìindii men."
  72,13,"E wonnde nde men nanunoo Alqur'aana fewnaynde nden, men gom…óinno nde. Kala gom…óin…óo Joomi mun, on hulataa …óuytaneede mo∆¥∆¥i mun, maa …ìeydaneede bon…ói goo e hoore adinoo…ói."
  72,14,"E wonnde hino e amen jul…óu…ói jebbiliranii Allah …óoftagol Mo, hino e amen kadi oo√±ii…ói seli goonga e √±ii…ìal. Kala non jebbiliranii ngii Allah …óoftagol golla ko mo∆¥∆¥i, ko …óin woni faandii…ói peewal e sawaaba."
  72,15,"Oo√±ii…ói e laawol goonga e √±ii…ìal …óin kan, …ói laatanike Jahannama on carmalle hu…ì…ìinir…óe nge, kannji e yim…ìe nanndu…ìe e majji."
  72,16,"Ko wano wahayiniraa non e makko fii dental jinna he…óinoo…ói Alqur'aana …óin, ko non kadi wahayiniraa e makko wonnde si jinna e yim…ìe √±ii…ìuno e laawol Islaamu ngol, …ìe gollitiri ko woni e mun kon, ko pellet, Allah ye…óayno …ìe ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam, O neeminira …ìe kadi ko seertu…ói."
  72,17,"Fii no Men ndaarndora …ìe …óam si …ìe yettay neema Allah on kaa hara …ìe yedday mo? Kala …óuurnii…óo Alqur'aana e waajuuji ko woni kon e mayre, Joomi makko naadoyay mo e lette sattu…óe …óe o townoytaa."
  72,18,"E wonnde juulir…óe …óen ko Allah tun heeranii. Wata on rewidu e Allah ton hay e gooto, haa wa'on wa Alyahuuda e Annasaara'en ka cuu…ói dewe ma…ì…ìe."
  72,19,"E wonnde tuma Muhammadu jeyaa…óo Allah (yo o his) darinoo himo rewa Joomi makko ka wi'etee : "Ba·π≠nu Nakhlah", jinnaaji …óin e…ì…ìuno fawondirgol e hoore makko, hakkee …ìi∆¥ondiro fii he…óagol himo jannga Alqur'aana."
  72,20,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe : Anndee ko Joomi am tun min mi rewata, mi kafidataa Mo e go…ó…óum goo no wa'i woo."
  72,21,"Maakan …ìe : min on mi waawanaa on du√±ogol lorra mo Allah hoddirani on, wanaa fii poo…óugol nafa mo Allah …óawi on."
  72,22,"Maakan …ìe : Hay gooto waawaa da…óndude lam e Allah si mi yeddii Mo; mi he…ìataa kadi ko woori Mo ∆¥oo√±orde ka mi moolotoo."
  72,23,"Ko mi waawani on, ko yottingol ko Allah nulin mi kon e mon, e nule Makko …óe O imminirimmi …óen e mon. Kala yeddu…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, hara depporde makko nden ko ka Yiite Jahannama, o lutta e magge, o yaltataa poomaa."
  72,24,"Heefer…ìe …ìen heddoray non e yeddugol haa si …ìe yi'oyii lette …óe …ìe kammbirananoo …óen aduna, ontuma …ìe anndoyto ko hombo …ìuri lo'ude ballo, …ìuri kadi fan…óude walloo…ìe."
  72,25,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe yeddu…ìe fii ummital : mi anndaa si tawii lette …óe kammbirana…óon …óen hino …ìadii, maa si tawii …óe happanaa lajal ngal Allah tun anndii fii mun."
  72,26,"Kanko senii…óo On ko O anndu…óo wirnii…ói …óin fow. Huunde e …óum wirnanaaki Mo. O ∆¥ellintinantaa wirnii…ói Makko …óin e hay e gooto. Ko Kanko tun heertorii ko O anndi fii mun kon."
  72,27,"Si wanaa mo Allah su…ìii e Nulaa…óo, O ∆¥ellintinay on …óon ko O muuyi woo, O immina Malaa'ikaa…ìe reenoo…ìe yeeso on Nulaa…óo ko ayna mo, fii wata mo wanaa Nulaa…óo ∆¥ellito e …óum."
  72,28,"Fii yo Nulaa…óo on anndu wonnde imminaa…ìe …ìen ko adii mbo …ìe yottinii Nule Joomi mun …óin, tawde Allah no hu…ìindori ko woni ka Malaa'ika e Nulaa…ìe fow e mun ganndal. Huunde wirnaaki Mo fii ma…ì…ìe. Himo mofti limoore kala huunde. Hay huunde suu…óaaki Senii…óo On."
